description: Best practices for using Vuetify UI components in Vue applications
globs: **/*.{vue,js,ts}
---

- Use Vuetify's grid system for responsive layouts that adapt to any screen, device, and size
- Customize themes using Vuetify's theme system to create a consistent and adaptable design
- Implement proper accessibility features provided by Vuetify to ensure usability across different devices
- Use Vuetify's built-in validation for forms to improve user experience and data integrity
- Optimize performance by lazy-loading components to reduce initial load time and improve adaptability